024/02/Final-Fantasy-7-Rebirth-review-copy-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Final-Fantasy-7-Rebirth-review-copy-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Final-Fantasy-7-Rebirth-review-copy-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Final-Fantasy-7-Rebirth-review-copy-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/square-enix">Square Enix</a>已确认许多正在开发的项目已被取消，工作室损失达 1.12 亿英镑。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/total-war-warhammer-3-thrones-of-decay-worth-it-3751859">《腐烂王座》是《全面战争：战锤 3》的回归</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一消息是通过史克威尔艾尼克斯本周早些时候与股东分享的<a href="https://www.hd.square-enix.com/eng/ir/pdf/20240430_01_en.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《承认特别损失通知</a>》发布的，而这些项目在上个财政年度末的 3 月份被放弃。</p><p>根据该通知，史克威尔艾尼克斯董事会“鉴于游戏世界目前正在发生的无数变化”做出了这一决定，该公司希望“修改游戏开发方法，以便更有效地开发游戏”。有选择地、有重点地配置发展资源。”</p><p>他们还补充说，“鉴于各种固有的不确定性”，1.12 亿英镑的损失可能会增加。</p><p> Square Enix 尚未确认哪些项目受到了这一决定的影响。早在 11 月，总裁桐生隆 (Takashi Kiryu) 就透露，他希望工作室减少对<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/dragon-quest">《勇者斗恶龙》</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy">《最终幻想》</a></em>等游戏的依赖（来自<em><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/square-enix-abandons-112m-of-in-development-projects-in-an-effort-to-improve-quality" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Eurogamer</a></em> ）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3365052" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3365052" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3365052" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1.jpg" alt="勇者斗恶龙宝藏。图片来源：史克威尔艾尼克斯。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/Dragon-Quest-Treasures-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3365052" class="wp-caption-text">勇者斗恶龙宝藏。图片来源：史克威尔艾尼克斯。</figcaption></figure><p> “游戏市场客户的品味已经多样化，客户开始享受各种类型的内容。市场在大片和独立游戏之间日益两极分化，但我觉得我们开发了许多介于两者之间的游戏。我想在未来做出更清晰的区分，”他补充道。</p><p>此前有报道称<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7-rebirth"><em>《最终幻想 7：重生》</em></a>表现不佳，销量仅为<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/final-fantasy-7-remake">《最终幻想 7：重制版》</a></em>的一半。 “我不认为这会对第三款游戏的范围产生重大影响，但这可能会导致 Square Enix 重新考虑其处理直接续集的方法，这些续集依赖于之前购买新游戏的基础标题，”分析师丹尼尔·艾哈迈德告诉<a href="https://www.inverse.com/gaming/square-enix-abandoned-games-ff7-rebirth-sales#:~:text=Final%20Fantasy%207%20Rebirth%20reportedly%20fell%20below%20sales%20targets%20for%20Square%20Enix.&amp;text=Without%20mid%2Dbudget%20titles%20to,be%20more%20important%20than%20ever." target="_blank" rel="noopener">Inverse</a> 。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="《最终幻想 VII 重生》最终预告片" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Q56cRDseTGQ?start=3&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>过去一周， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/flaming-fowl-studios">Flaming Fowl</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/people-can-fly">People Can Fly</a>等工作室<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/outriders-studio-people-can-fly-cancels-co-op-action-rpg-project-dagger-3751114">因游戏“缺乏资金”而</a>取消了正在开发的项目，而<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/grand-theft-auto">侠盗猎车手</a></em>发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/take-two">Take-Two</a>也证实已<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/grand-theft-auto-publisher-take-two-lays-off-hundreds-of-staff-and-cancels-games-3618889">解雇了数百名员工，并取消了游戏数量。</a></p><p>一月份，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>确认将解雇<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox">Xbox</a>和新收购的<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/1900-activision-blizzard-and-xbox-staff-laid-off-survival-game-cancelled-3577037">1900 名员工</a>，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/riot-games">Riot Games</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/league-of-legends-developer-halts-spin-offs-amid-mass-layoffs-3575645">则解雇了 500 多名员工</a>，并取消了所有<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/league-of-legends">《英雄联盟》</a></em>衍生游戏的开发。接下来的一个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/disco-elysium">《极乐迪斯科》</a>开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/za-um">ZA/UM</a>裁员了四分之一。</p><p>在其他消息中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/microsoft">微软</a>已确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/xbox-confirms-june-showcase-alongside-a-secret-direct-3752315">Xbox 游戏展示会将于下个月举行</a>，同时还有神秘的直面会。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/square-enix-abandons-112million-of-in-development-projects-in-bid-to-streamline-output-3752364">Square Enix 放弃了 1.12 亿英镑的开发中项目，以“精简”产出，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
